---
title: Tomato Garlic Ragu with Beef, Parmesan Cheese, and Chili Oil
description: Everyone loves the deep beefy flavor of a ragu sauce, but who actually has the time to wait hours while it slowly simmers? Fortunately, a dash of soy sauce does the trick. Believe it or not, this secret ingredient adds a unique umami touch for that enviable slow-cooked taste.
